original_title: DeSantis awards posthumous medals to Jimmy Buffett, 4 other Floridians | Fox News
article_summary: Florida Governor Ron DeSantis awards the Governor's Medal of Freedom posthumously to five Floridians, including Jimmy Buffett, Lincoln Diaz-Balart, Bob Graham, Buddy MacKay, and John Thrasher, recognizing their significant contributions to the state.</s>
